# Spellcasters Community API Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env or .env.local to use it locally.
# This file is loaded automatically via direnv if using .envrc

# Currently, the local build scripts do not require any mandatory environment variables to run.
# This file serves as a template for future environment-specific configurations
# (e.g., CI/CD tokens, specialized debug flags, or external integrations).

# Example:
# ENVIRONMENT=development
# DEBUG=true
